se.cbb.jprime.topology

Class ReconciledRBTreeGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.topology.ReconciledRBTreeGenerator

  • public class ReconciledRBTreeGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Given a guest-to-host leaf map and a host tree, provides means for generating a reconciled guest tree. See also UniformRBTreeGenerator.

    In the future, this could include e.g. a method for the most parsimonious reconciliation.

        Simplistic generator of a reconciled guest tree, which just joins all guest tree leaves as in-paralogs, then connects those subtrees congruently with host tree.
        Parameters:
        GSMap - guest-to-host tree leaf map.
        S - host tree topology.
        SNames - leaf/vertex names of S.
        paramName - the parameter name of the guest topology G to be created.
        prng - pseudo-random number generator.
        Returns:
        guest tree topology and its names map.
